She is a great hair dresser and knows her stuff!
If you want a great hair stylist with an amazing personality this is the right one for you!

I am very picky when it comes to someone cutting or styling my hair but Alice is Hands down the best hair dresser I have ever had!
I have been here twice and both times where amazing!

Very few hair dressers have been able to give me the cut that I've asked for.
Alice on the other hand is not afraid to get in there and give me the rock star layers that I love.
She is not only an amazing hairdresser, she is an amazing person and I would recommend her, hands down, as the best Vegas has to offer.

